channel.title: Another deltascape question
channel.description: Hey guys I need help again this time it's with my pure command, When I type pure it gives me 99 everything in every skill besides def and prayer but I only want it giving them 99atk.99str,99hp,99range,99mage and it gives all the other skills to so plz help :)?

item.title: Another deltascape question
item.dc:creator: @xmaker1 xmaker1
item.description:
@xmaker1 wrote:

Place this with the rest of your commands.

if(command.equalsIgnoreCase("master") && playerRights >= 2) { for(int i = 0; i < 21; i++) { addSkillXP(14000000, i); } }
Where it says “master” put command name in eg. “pure”
replace the “i” in the code the with the number of the skill you want and do that for every stat eg.

addSkillXP(14000000, 1);
addSkillXP(14000000, 2);
addSkillXP(14000000, 3);
